snippet.title: Soda Dungeon 2 [PC] Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Like the original, Soda Dungeon 2 is a turn-based dungeon crawler, which sees players recruiting a team of intrepid adventurers to raid dungeons on their behalf.


More details here: https://worthplaying.com/game/13993/


Soda Dungeon 2 launches on PC (Steam), iOS, and Android on July 9, 2020 and will be free to play. You can also play it today on Android via Google Play Early Access!
